here is the statebystate economic report 
card issued today by the corporation for enterprise development a 
private nonprofit research group 
the grades a b c d and f are in four areas 
economic performance shown here as per this includes such 
factors as employment earnings job quality poverty income 
distribution crime and environmental health and safety 
business vitality shown here as vit this refers to the 
competitiveness of existing businesses industrial diversity and 
the ability to generate new jobs in new businesses 
economic capacity shown here as cap this covers human 
technological physical and financial resources 
policy shown here as pol this measures policies on taxes 
education infrastructure business support and development and 
policies toward disadvantaged communities and individuals 
