wednesday he favors reunification as quickly as possible 
the negotiations quickened this week after west germanys 
central bank said it was recommending a 21 conversion of east 
german marks to west german marks as part of a currency union 
east german parties united in opposition to that proposal 
calling for a direct 11 conversion to ease the withdrawal pains of 
unemployment and high prices as east germany sheds its socialist 
system 
west germany said wednesday it wants a pact on monetary union by 
early next month but the east germans are expected to be tough 
negotiators once serious talks begin 
