raised his stature with the smaller parties which have often 
described him as a puppet of west german chancellor helmut kohl 
but the social democrats still are opposed to the more 
conservative elements in de maizieres alliance much of the 
wrangling has been over the distribution of cabinet posts in a new 
government 
the social democrats who favor more emphasis on environmental 
and social issues have asked for the education foreign and labor 
ministries 
