excise taxes for that purpose 
for example rep dan rostenkowski dill chairman of the 
house ways and means committee has outlined a comprehensive plan 
that includes higher taxes for gasoline beer wine and cigarettes 
as well as increased income taxes and a oneyear freeze on social 
security benefits 
the peat marwick report said that while a 20billionayear 
boost in excise taxes would raise the tax burden of the average 
american by 19 percent the onethird of people with the lowest 
incomes would see a 65 percent increase 
