much further than overturning the supreme court decisions 
it is in my view a radical reworking of our nations basic 
employment antidiscrimination law hatch said hiring the most 
qualified person will not be a satisfactory explanation if an 
employers numbers are not right 
sen nancy kassebaum rkan said the panel should find 
harmony and conciliation in the workplace but that under the 
legislation we simply add litigation 
several other republicans however are cosponsors of the 
measure 
