said he expects to be accompanied to the border 185 miles from 
warsaw by a highlevel lithuanian government delegation 
damato said he will try to cross the border with a lithuanian 
visa despite the fact that the soviet union does not recognize the 
republic as an independent nation 
the soviet union has ordered western diplomats out of lithuania 
evicted foreign journalists and forbidden traffic at the single 
polishlithuanian border crossing it is lithuanias only direct 
land access to the rest of europe 
