he was adopting a nevada state bar disciplinary boards 
recommendation that claiborne be reinstated 
claiborne 73 was convicted of failing to report more than 
106000 on his 1979 and 1980 tax returns he was removed from his 
lifetime post oct 10 1986 after the us senate convicted him on 
three of four articles of impeachment 
claiborne claimed at his impeachment hearing that he was the 
victim of prosecutors he had offended while on the bench 
he served 17 months of a twoyear prison term and resumed his 
law practice in state court shortly after he was released 
broomfield had denied claiborne permission to practice in 
federal court in september 1988 but allowed him to apply again 
last september 
