convicted for his role in a january 1987 coup attempt 
cacacho said the report of the escape was withheld until 
thursday so as not to jeopardize the search 
the coup attempt in january 1987 was the third bid to topple 
mrs aquino who took power in 1986 the latest and bloodiest 
attempt was in december 
