the better off we are we cant wait for this to become a national 
issue i can see it now the today show and everyone else would be 
running programs on us he said 
evans said a report issued wednesday by a government panel of 
scientists leaves no question that logging must stop across a large 
section of national forests in order to save the spotted owl 
