community 
he said the reforms would benefit not only the united states and 
japan but also the whole world serve to prevent the rise of 
protectionism and thus contribute to the steady development of the 
world economy 
i ask for the understanding and cooperation of the people of 
my country kaifu said 
on japans promise to revise laws protecting small retailers 
