a strong earthquake 
shook a section of the marianas islands on friday and rattled 
windows 200 miles away authorities said there were no reports of 
injury or serious damage 
the quake occurred at 715 am 515 pm thursday edt and 
registered 74 on the richter scale according to bruce presgrave 
a spokesman for the national earthquake information service in 
golden colo 
the epicenter was 138 miles northeast of saipan near the island 
of anatahan in the western pacific 
a reading of 74 would make it a major earthquake but the 
only information we have is that it was felt on guam presgrave 
said weve had no reports of damage at all 
we felt it for about 10 seconds everything shook said 
andrew mazella program director at radio station ksai in saipan 
the quake rattled windows and dishes in guam 220 miles southwest 
of the epicenter 
the quake slammed a 15foot wave into tinian a tiny island 
south of saipan and pushed 5 feet of water into houses on tanapag 
a village on saipan island said felix sasamoto civil defense 
coordinator for the islands 
some moorings broke loose in tinian but no other damage was 
reported sasamoto said 
on tuesday all 21 residents of anatahan closest to the 
epicenter abandoned the island after a volcano there showed signs 
of erupting 
a navy crew from guam was checking the volcano friday but 
geologists said the quake and volcanic activity apparently were 
unrelated 
this is different from the volcanic activity that has been 
occurring in the islands said presgrave 
anatahan and saipan are part of the northern marianas chain just 
north of guam about 1500 miles east of the philippines 
the richter scale is a measure of ground motion as recorded on 
seismographs every increase of one number means a tenfold increase 
in magnitude 
an earthquake of 6 on the richter scale can cause severe damage 
in the local area a 7 reading is a major earthquake capable 
of widespread heavy damage 8 is a great quake capable of 
tremendous damage 
the san francisco earthquake of 1906 which occurred before the 
richter scale was devised has been estimated at 83 on the richter 
scale 
